え、<br>新たな目標実現のために</b></p>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"p-read__text\">百年以上の歴史を誇る医薬品・医療機器の老舗卸。<br>\n\t\t\t地元密着のキメ細かなサービス提供により<br class=\"u-hidden-medium\">高い信頼を獲得しています！<br>\n\t\t\tその秘訣はお客様との密接な関係づくり。<br>\n\t\t\t●<br>\n\t\t\t自分が主人公になってそれぞれのストーリーを展開し<br>\n\t\t\t次なる目標に向けて一歩一歩確実に<br class=\"u-hidden-medium\">私たちと前進してみませんか。</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"c-band\">\n\t\t<section class=\"p-top-menu\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"c-container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card js-move\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__object\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t    <source media=\"(min-width: 980px)\" srcset=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/iwabuchi-recruit/assets/dist/images/topmesse_lg.jpg?201907\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t     <img src=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/iwabuchi-recruit/assets/dist/images/topmesse.jpg?201907\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t </picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"c-card__title\"><span class=\"c-card__en\">TOP MESSAGE</span></h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-top-menu__meta\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>岩渕薬品株式会社<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t代表取締役社長<span class=\"p-top-menu__name\">岩渕 琢磨</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p-top-menu__text\">若手社員が次の100年をリードする存在<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t若い時から新しいことにチャレンジできる風土をつくっていた<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t当社で積極的に活躍していただける力を求めています</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"c-card__btn\"><a href=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/top-message\" class=\"c-btn\">READ MORE</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t<section class=\"p-top-menu\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"c-container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card js-move\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__object\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 980px)\" srcset=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/iwabuchi-recruit/assets/dist/images/discus_lg.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/iwabuchi-recruit/assets/dist/images/sp_discus.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"c-card__title\"><span class=\"c-card__en\">SPECIAL DISCUSSION</span></h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"p-top-menu__meta\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>代表取締役社長<span class=\"p-top-menu__name\">岩渕 琢磨</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"p-top-menu__accent\">×</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t代表取締役専務<span class=\"p-top-menu__name\">岩渕 裕樹</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p-top-menu__text\">創業100年を超える老舗卸の岩渕薬品<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t新卒採用にあたり、<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t求める人物像とは・・・医薬品卸業の営業の魅力と思いを語る</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"c-card__btn\"><a href=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/special-discussion\" class=\"c-btn\">READ MORE</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"p-parallax \">\n\t\t<div class=\"p-parallax__text\"><span class=\"p-parallax__text-large\">MS</span>Marketing Specialist</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"c-container\">\n\t\t<section class=\"p-index-menu\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"p-index-menu__title\">INTERVIEW</h2>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-grid c-grid_collapse\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-grid__u c-grid__u_medium_1of2 c-grid__u_large_1of3\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card js-move js-fade\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__object\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/interview/megumi-sunaga/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/sunaga.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p-index-menu__catch\">女性MSの先輩として後輩をサポート</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"c-card__title\">須永　恵</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>営業統括本部　<br>営業支援部　係長｜2005年入社</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"c-card__btn\"><a href=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/rec