r\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"c-grid c-grid_collapse\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-grid__u c-grid__u_medium_1of2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card p-large-card js-move\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__object\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 980px)\" srcset=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/iwabuchi-recruit/assets/dist/images/yamada_lg.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/iwabuchi-recruit/assets/dist/images/yamada.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"c-card__title\">MESSAGE</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p-large-card__catch\">岩渕薬品初の女性部長として学生のみなさんへ</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p-large-card__text\">時代の変化に柔軟に対応し<br>新しいことに躊躇することなくチャレンジできる<br>元気ある学生を求めています</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"c-card__btn\"><a href=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/message\" class=\"c-btn\">READ MORE</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-grid__u c-grid__u_medium_1of2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card p-large-card p-large-card_light p-large-card_bottom js-move\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__object\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 980px)\" srcset=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/iwabuchi-recruit/assets/dist/images/culture_lg.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://www.iwabuchi-net.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/iwabuchi-recruit/assets/dist/images/culture.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-card__body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"c-card__title\">EMPLOYEE BENEFITS</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p-large-card__catch\">福利厚生｜研修制度</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p-large-card__text\">女性がいきいき活躍できる働きやすい環境への取り組みから<br>営業職の知識とスキルアップのために多くの研修を用意、<br>充実した教育体制を整えています</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"c-card__btn\"><a href=\"http://www.